Author: starskey
Title: [ANN] [PRE-ICO] - ALCHEMYBYTE (ALB) Dual Value Token-Asset Backed-PRE-ICO LIVE!
Body: One Project, One ICO, Two Tokens  Best Features of Two Blockchains  AlchemyByte™: An Asset Backed Digital Currency on Waves SL#Byte™: A Partnership Program on Ethereum  AlchemyByte is a new digital token backed both by a portfolio of other cryptoassets whose value is determinable and auditable, and by the development work of its laboratory – AlchemySmartLab (www.alchemysmartlab.com) which is already in operation.  The Token Issuer undertakes to asset back the token issue by maintaining the Master Trust’s balance sheet at between 70% and 75% of the total value of the Master Trust in other cryptocurrencies and between 25% and 30% in other cryptocurrency related assets, for example shares in or loans to miners, platforms, exchanges, app developers, crypto developers et cetera.   Main Features of AlchemyByte Built in Value Guaranteed Fork Protection Unique Protection for Token Holders Determinable Fair Price Asset-Backed   Built in Value     Unique Protection for Token Holders   Asset-Backed    Whitepaper now published on website  https://www.alchemybyte.com  Social Media Links https://www.facebook.com/AlchemyByte/ https://twitter.com/AlchemyByte https://www.instagram.com/alchemybyte/    Launch Timetable 16th October Announcement & Whitepaper Published Pre-Sale date to be announced shortly Additional Incentive for Pre-Sale Buyers – SL#Byte    Thanks for reading!

Author: starskey
Title: [ANN] [PRE-ICO] - ALCHEMYBYTE (ALB) Dual Value Token-Asset Backed-PRE-ICO LIVE!
Body: As part of our normal release process, we have identified a further improvement we had wished to make before releasing the pre-ICO on its expected release date. Therefore, AlchemyByte’s pre-ICO was delayed. Investors will appreciate this decision has been taken out of an abundance of caution and in light of the upsurge in ICO hacking attempts that have occurred recently: CoinDash (July 2017), Enigma (Aug. 2017) and EtherParty/FUEL (Oct. 2017). The additional improvements have been made and they have now passed our stringent quality assurance tests.  We are proud to announce that our pre-sale ICO will go live as at the 2nd of January 2018 at 1600 CET.  We hope that you will see value in our projects and looking forward to answering any questions. You may also review the whitepaper on www.alchemybyte.com
